</HEADER>

<F P=100> North Korea </F>
<H3> <TI>   Activities Celebrate Kim Il-Song's Birthday </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Activities Celebrate Kim Il-Song's Birthday </PHRASE></F></HT>
<H4>    Songs Presented by Overseas Koreans </H4>

<F P=102> SK1304113594 Pyongyang KCNA in English 1103 GMT 13 Apr 94 </F>
<F P=103> SK1304113594 </F>
<F P=104>  Pyongyang KCNA </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Pyongyang, April 13 (KCNA) -- Loud songs of loyalty 
sung by overseas Koreans are ringing out from the stages of the 
12th April Spring Friendship Art Festival which is open in 
Pyongyang in celebration of the birthday of the great leader 
President Kim Il-song. 
  Participating in the festival are an art troupe of Koreans 
in 
Japan, an art troupe of Koreans in China and an art troupe of 
the International Federation of Koreans for Reunification. 
  The art troupe of Koreans in Japan is putting on stage "Song 
of Best Wishes Presented by the 700,000 Compatriots" at the 
Pyongyang Grand Theatre. 
  The tune, song and dance "Holiday" is the curtain-raiser of 
their colorful program consisting of soloes, choruses and 
dances. In "Holiday" the performers say that the 700,000 
Koreans in Japan wholeheartedly extend congratulations to the 
great leader, becoming flowers of loyalty and filial piety, 
calling the spring holiday in April, the month of his birth, a 
spring holiday of Korea, a spring holiday of the sun. 
  Hong Yong-wol, a "Kim Il-song Prize" winner and people's 
actress, passionately sings the song "Leader, Please Accept our 
Wishes" to be acclaimed by the audience. 
  Merited actor Yi Yong-su in the solo "A Happy Memory" sings 
loudly that Marshal Kim Chong-il is the father, saying that his 
deep loving care and broad smiles always give new courage and 
show a bright road. 
  The dancers in the dance "Spring Flowers" present on a vivid 
canvas the loyal hearts of the people in the homeland and the 
700,000 Koreans in Japan who will always hold the dear leader 
Marshal Kim Chong-il in high esteem to the tune of the song 
"Flowers in Full Bloom All Over the Country", with light red 
fans in their hands. 
  The Korean artistes from China are putting on stage the 
narration and song "Let us Sing of our Bliss in Having Sagacious 
Leader" and other numbers, touching the heart's cord of the 
audience. The performers loudly sing of the pride and 
happiness of the Koreans who are enjoying all the blessings of 
the world, though they are living in an alien land, as they have 
the great leader and the dear leader. 
  The performers of a woman solo and trio, in the song "Our 
General is the Greatest", highly laud the greatness of General 
Kim Chong-il who is the dearest father of the soldiers of the 
Korean People's Army, who calls at posts among bushy young pine 
trees and travels with them through the sky and the sea and who 
deals a sledge-hammer blow at the enemy. 
  The artistes of the International Federation of Koreans for 
Reunification are putting on stage the dance "Night of 
Pyongyang, Don't Advance", the female duet "The Old Home in the 
Snow," the female solo "I am Your Eternal Son" and other numbers. 
  The dance "Night of Pyongyang, Don't Advance" makes the 
audience feel the national pride of living in the socialist 
homeland under the guidance of the great leader and the dear 
leader. 
  The audience are deeply impressed by the performances of 
overseas Korean artistes who find it hard to repress their 
longing and reverence, embraced in the bosom of the great leader 
Generalissimo Kim Il-song and the dear leader Marshal Kim 
Chong-il. 

</TEXT>

</DOC>

<DOC>
<DOCNO> FBIS4-5924 </DOCNO>
