<F P=100> North Korea </F>
<H3> <TI>   Kim Il-song Meets With Visiting Delegations </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Kim Il-song Meets With Visiting Delegations </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   SK1504103594 Pyongyang KCNA in English 1028 GMT 15 Apr 94 </F>
<F P=103> SK1504103594 </F>
<F P=104>  Pyongyang KCNA </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Pyongyang, April 15 (KCNA) -- The great leader 
Comrade Kim Il-song, general secretary of the Central Committee 
of the Workers' Party of Korea [WPK] and president of the 
Democratic People's Republic of Korea, today received foreign 
high-level delegations and delegates at the Kumsusan Assembly 
Hall who paid a congratulatory call on him. 
  They were a delegation of the National Democratic Congress 
of 
Ghana headed by its general secretary Huudu Yahaya, a delegation 
of the Socialist Party of Kazakhstan headed by its co-chairman 
P. V. Svoik, a delegation of the Workers' Party of Ireland 
headed by its general secretary Pat Quearney, general secretary 
of the Workers' Party of Turkey Yalsin Buyukdagli, a delegation 
of the Liaoning Provincial Committee of the Communist Party of 
China headed by its secretary Gu Jinchi, a delegation of the 
October 8 Revolutionary Movement of Brazil headed by member of 
the political commission and secretary of the movement Sergio 
Rubens, vice-president of the Socialist Workers' Party of 
Romania Maria Lazar, vice-chairman of the Liberal Democratic 
Party and deputy speaker of the state Duma of the Federation 
Council of Russia A. D. Vengerovskiy and his entourage, a 
delegation of the Maritime Territorial Committee of the 
Communist Party [CP] of the Russian Federation headed by its 
first secretary V. V. Grishukov, first secretary of the 
Khabarovsk Territorial Committee of the Communist Party of the 
Russian Federation L. A. Golub, a delegation of the Amur 
Regional Committee of the CP of the Russian Federation headed by 
its first secretary G. E. Gamza, a delegation of the Japan-Korea 
Friendship Data Center headed by Yoshiyuki Oe, chairman of the 
center and president of the S.B.B. Company, Ltd., of Japan, 
director general of the International Institute of the Chuche 
Idea Shuhachi Inoue, secretary general of the World Federation 
of Trade Unions Alexandr Jarikov, a delegation of the 
secretariat of the Society for the Study of the Chuche Idea of 
Japanese Teachers headed by Masagazu Yokobori, advisor and 
secretary general of the Japan Liaison Council of Societies for 
the Study of Kim Chong-il's Works, a delegation of the Kim 
Chong-suk Kindergarten in Dalandzadgad City, Omnogov Province, 
Mongolia, headed by its superintendent Altantuya, a delegation 
of the Karachi branch of the Pakistan-Korea Friendship 
Association headed by Abdul Razak Molai and chairman of the 
Mongolian Study Centre of the Chuche Idea Y. O. Maxim. 
  Present on the occasion were Hwang Chang-yop, secretary of 
the WPK Central Committee and officials concerned. 
  The guests presented a flower basket to President Kim 
Il-song 
in celebration of his birthday and wished him long life in good 
health. 
  President Kim Il-song expressed thanks for this and had a 
cordial and friendly talk with them. 

</TEXT>

