BFN 

  [Text] Pyongyang, April 15 (KCNA) -- Overseas Koreans on a 
visit to the socialist homeland paid a congratulatory call on 
the great leader President Kim Il-song today. 
  The visitors included the congratulatory group of Koreans in 
Japan for celebrating April 15 led by Yi Chin-kyu, first vice- 
chairman of the Central Standing Committee of the General 
Association of Korean Residents in Japan (Chongnyon), the 
delegation of old cadres of Chongnyon led by Paek Chong-won, 
chairman of the Sports Federation of Koreans in Japan, and other 
delegations of Chongnyon, the congratulatory group of the 
International Federation of Koreans for Reunification for 
celebrating April 15 led by its vice-chairman Chu Yong-il, the 
