Alliance for the Country's Reunification (Pomminnyon) for 
celebrating April 15 led by Nam Su-nam, first vice- chairman of 
the Pomminnyon headquarters of Koreans in China, the 
congratulatory group of the Organisation of Korean Citizens in 
Russia for celebrating April 15 led by Chae Chong-man, and Choe 
Hong-hui, president of the International Taekwon-do Federation, 
