<F P=100> North Korea </F>
<H3> <TI>   Receives PRENSA LATINA Head </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Receives PRENSA LATINA Head </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   SK1304121194 Pyongyang KCNA in English 1124 GMT 13 Apr 94 </F>
<F P=103> SK1304121194 </F>
<F P=104>  Pyongyang KCNA </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Pyongyang, April 13 (KCNA) -- The great leader 
President Kim Il-song today received Pedro Margolles Villanueva, 
director general of the PRENSA LATINA of Cuba, and his companion 
on a visit to Korea. 
  Present on the occasion were Vice-premier and Foreign 
Minister Kim Yong-nam, Director General of the Korean Central 
News Agency Kim Ki-yong and Cuban Ambassador E.P. to Korea Jose 
Ramon Rodriguez Varona. 
  The guests warmly congratulated President Kim Il-song on his 
birthday and wished him a long life in good health. 
  President Kim Il-song expressed thanks for this, conversed 
with the guests in a cordial and friendly atmosphere and 
answered questions put by the director general. 
  President Kim Il-song arranged a luncheon for them. 

</TEXT>

</DOC>

