<F P=103> SK1704090294 </F>
<F P=104>  Pyongyang KCNA </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Pyongyang, April 17 (KCNA) -- The construction of 
the Sinyon Joint-Venture Company run by Sinuiju City, a border 
city in the Northwestern part of Korea, and by the Yanbian 
Autonomous Region of China was completed and it went into 
operation on the occasion of the significant April fete. 
  The company will help increase the production of daily 
necessities and develop economic exchange and friendly and 
cooperative relations between Korea and China. 
  Its commissioning ceremony took place in Sinuiju on April 
15. 

