BFN 

    [Editorial Report] Pyongyang Central Broadcasting Network 
in Korean at 0500 GMT on 14 April reports on a banquet held at 
the DPRK Embassy in the PRC on 11 April to celebrate Kim 
Il-song's birthday. 
  Present at the banquet were Ding Guangen, member of the 
political bureau of the CPC Central Committee and member of the 
CPC Secretariat; Li Shuzheng, head of the International Liaison 
Department of the CPC Central Committee; Han Zhubin, minister of 
