<H3> <TI>   Kim Il-song Receives Flowers for Birthday </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Kim Il-song Receives Flowers for Birthday </PHRASE></F></HT>
<H4>    From PLO's 'Arafat </H4>

<F P=102> SK1204233494 Pyongyang KCNA in English 2241 GMT 12 Apr 94 </F>
<F P=103> SK1204233494 </F>
<F P=104>  Pyongyang KCNA </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Pyongyang, April 12 (KCNA) -- Yasir 'Arafat, 
president of the State of Palestine and chairman of the 
Executive Committee of the Palestine Liberation Organization 
(PLO), sent a floral basket to President Kim Il-song of the 
Democratic People's Republic of Korea, on his birthday. 
  The floral basket was handed Tuesday to an official 
concerned 
by Palestinian Ambassador to Korea Shahir Mohammed. 

</TEXT>

</DOC>

