BFN 

  [Text] Pyongyang, April 18 (KCNA) -- The great leader 
President Kim Il-song received congratulatory messages on the 
occasion of his birthday from "Mindan"-lining [as received] 
compatriots living in Tokyo, Osaka, Kyoto, Hokkaido, Ibaraki and 
other regions of Japan and South Koreans staying in Japan. 
  Noting that President Kim Il-song has built Korean-style 
socialism centred on the popular masses in the Northern half of 
Korea and wisely led the struggle to accelerate the 
reunification of the country, the messages express the 
determination to wage a vigorous struggle in response to the 
10-point programme of the great unity of the whole nation for 
the reunification of the country. 
  The messages sincerely wish President Kim Il-song a long 
life 
in good health. 

