BFN 

  [Text] Pyongyang, April 18 (KCNA) -- President Kim Il-song 
of the Democratic People's Republic of Korea received messages 
of greetings on the occasion of his birthday from Lilic Zoran, 
president of the Federal Republic of Yugoslavia; France Albert 
Rene, president of the Republic of Seychelles; Gnassingbe 
Eyadema, president of the Republic of Togo; Sani Abacha, head of 
