Republic of Pakistan; Hafiz al-Asad, president of the Syrian 
Arab Republic; Umar Hasan Ahmed al-Bashir, president of the 
Republic of Sudan; Violeta Barrios de Chamorro, president of the 
Republic of Nicaragua; and Ilyas Harawi, president of the 
Republic of Lebanon. 
  The messages extend warmest congratulations to President Kim 
Il- song and wish him a long life in good health. 
  They express the belief that the friendly and cooperative 
relations between the Korean people and the peoples of the 
abovesaid countries would grow stronger and develop. 

</TEXT>

