<H3> <TI>   Economic Restrictions on South Africa Lifted </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Economic Restrictions on South Africa Lifted </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   BK1804083594 Rangoon THE NEW LIGHT OF BURMA in English 31 
Mar 94 p 12 </F>

<F P=103> BK1804083594 </F>
<F P=104>  Rangoon THE NEW LIGHT OF BURMA </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

<F P=106> ["Press Communique"] </F>
  [Text] The Government of the Union of Myanmar [Burma], 
pursuant to the political and constitutional process in South 
Africa, which have ensured the elimination of apartheid and in 
compliance with the United Nations General Assembly resolution 
lifting economic sanctions against that country, has decided to 
end the economic restrictions and prohibitions it had hitherto 
imposed on South Africa with effect from 23 March 1994. 

</TEXT>

