Democratic 
Party of 
Japan [SDPJ] 


Shinseito      50            22          25        15            8 

Komeito        30            2           24        18            4 

Sakigake       31            10          17        13            9 

Democratic     11            1           11        3             2 
Socialist 
Party [DSP] 

Others         20            5           9         8             17 

Opposition Parties 

