Communist Party of China have visited Mongolia at the invitation 
of the ruling Mongolian People's Revolutionary Party (MPRP). 
The MPRP has not so far informed about their arrival and stay 
here. However one of the independent newspapers of Mongolia is 
planning to make public the stay of party functioners from the 
Communist Party of China in the country, publicating their names 
in one of its nearest issues. 

