<H4>    More Join Strikers </H4>

<F P=102> OW1504174694 Ulaanbaatar MONTSAME in English 1439 GMT 15 Apr 
94--FOR OFFICIAL USE ONLY </F>

<F P=103> OW1504174694 </F>
<F P=104>  Ulaanbaatar MONTSAME </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Ulaanbaatar, April 15 (OANA-MONTSAME) -- Another 
nine people have joined the going on here at the main square of 
the Mongolian capital political hunger strike demanding the 
resignation of the government which is carried out by the 
Mongolian Democratic Association, its number reaching now 31. 
So far any information referring to a worsening health state of 
anyone participating in the action since 13 April has not been 
reported. 

</TEXT>

