<F P=100> ANNEX </F>
<F P=101> Mongolia </F>
<H3> <TI>   MPRP Parliamentary Group Supports Government </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    MPRP Parliamentary Group Supports Government </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   OW1504173094 Ulaanbaatar MONTSAME in English 1437 GMT 15 Apr 
94--FOR OFFICIAL USE ONLY </F>

<F P=103> OW1504173094 </F>
