<F P=101> Mongolia </F>
<H3> <TI>   Herbal Vaccine Developed Against Meningitis </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Herbal Vaccine Developed Against Meningitis </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   OW1604141294 Ulaanbaatar MONTSAME in English 1206 GMT 16 Apr 
94--FOR OFFICIAL USE ONLY </F>

<F P=103> OW1604141294 </F>
<F P=104>  Ulaanbaatar MONTSAME </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Ulaanbaatar, April 16 (OANA-MONTSAME) -- The 
pharmacological and cosmetological "Monos" company has 
manufactured from the medicinal herbs for the first time in 
Mongolia a vaccine against the infectious meningitis getting 
recently a wide spread in the country. The new preparation is 
coming on the market in the drugstores of the Mongolian capital. 

</TEXT>

