  [Text] Kuala Lumpur, April 19 (OANA-BERNAMA) -- Czech 
Foreign Affairs Minister Josef Zieleniec arrived here Tuesday 
for a two-day official visit to Malaysia. Zieleniec, 
accompanied by his wife Pavla Zieleniecova, and an entourage of 
