<H3> <TI>   Ministry on Issue of `Discontinuing' Team Spirit </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Ministry on Issue of `Discontinuing' Team Spirit </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   SK1704022394 Seoul CHOSON ILBO in Korean 17 Apr 94 p 2 </F>
<F P=103> SK1704022394 </F>
<F P=104>  Seoul CHOSON ILBO </F>
<F P=105>  Korean </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

<F P=106> [By Yu Yong-won] </F>
  [Text] The ROK Defense Ministry stated on 16 April that it 
would consider discontinuing the Team Spirit exercise if North 
Korea accepts [suyong] additional inspections from the 
International Atomic Energy Agency and if progress is made in 
resolving the nuclear issue. The Defense Ministry reportedly 
mapped out this plan because the government abandoned the plan 
on the exchange of special envoys. 

</TEXT>

